ActCustoms Tariff
SubjectCIFTA Tariff Preference Regulations
PrecisCIFTA TARIFF PREFERENCES REGULATIONS in order to repeal and replace the CIFTA Tariff Preference Regulations (SOR/97-64) and allow eligible goods that are not shipped directly between Israel and Canada to retain the eligibility for preferential tariff rates provided the goods remain under customs control in third countries.
